<br>
MR determines the duration a charm can hold.  The lower the MR(for example Dictate the chanter permanent 45 second unbreakable charm has -1000 ) the longer the charm holds.  They changed COD MR from - 50 to -10 so it will not hold nearly as long as it used to and will break more often.  <br>
